Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.17,0:23:22.51,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}我也仍想爱下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.72,0:23:25.68,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\t(1900,2400,\3c&HC2B44C&)}夜色满溢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.68,0:23:27.68,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HC2B44C&\blur3}在这个不知余年多少的今天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.89,0:23:35.90,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HC2B44C&\blur3}我只想要你能让我继续思念你
